item.title: HL-L2350DW Mono Laser Printer | Brother Australia
item.description:
HL-L2350DW Mono Laser Printer | Brother Australia

Desktop friendly printer for your home or small office. Featuring up to 3,000 page replaceable high-yield toner & wireless connectivity.
This is the printer recommended by the Tech Guys: Leo Laporte and Micah Sargent.
